    "body": "Conflux is very like ethereum, but have a several difference:\r\n1. Our RPC is not compatible with eth.\r\n2. When creating transaction two new fields is needed: `epochHeight`, `storageLimit`\r\n3. Our address is very different from eth hex40 address, is a base32 checksum address for example: `cfxtest:ach727k1wt7kmj633hc1fcrrgbajmargkaxyycf6ee`\r\nbut every conflux address can convert to hex40 address for example: `0x8fdC753793fA952399c9C57289ad30408501a648`\r\n\r\n",
