    "body": "For the differece 1 we can create a RPC bridge to convert Conflux RPC to eth RPC, which seems can cover most truffle used RPC:\r\n\r\n* eth_blockNumber\r\n* net_version\r\n* eth_accounts\r\n* eth_getBlockByNumber\r\n* eth_getCode\r\n* eth_call\r\n* eth_estimateGas\r\n* eth_sendTransaction\r\n* eth_sendRawTransaction\r\n* eth_getTransactionReceipt\r\n* eth_getTransactionByHash\r\n* eth_getBalance\r\n\r\nMaybe some RPC used by truffle is not list here.",
